<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278296>
    dc:description "FIGURES 9 – 13. Brachyptera kontschani sp. n. (Figs. 9 – 10, 13) and B. dinarica Aubert (Figs. 11 – 12) — 9: head and pronotum; 10 – 11: female pregenital plate and vulvar sclerites, ventral view; 12: distal plate of the male ventral process of epiproct, dorsal view; 13: female terminalia, ventral view — scales 1 mm; Figs. 9, 13 to scale 1, Figs. 10 – 12 to scale 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278296/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278295>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 8. Male terminalia of Brachyptera kontschani sp. n. — 1: male terminalia, dorsal view; 2: male terminalia, lateral view; 3: male terminalia, ventral view; 4: paraprocts, ventral view; 5: paraprocts, apical view; 6: distal plate of ventral process of epiproct, dorsal view; 7: distal plate of ventral process of epiproct, lateral view; 8: distal plate of ventral process of epiproct, dorso-lateral view — scales 1 mm; Figs. 1 – 3 to scale 1, Figs. 4 – 8 to scale 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278295/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.278297>
    dc:description "FIGURES 14 – 15. Distribution of Brachyptera kontschani sp. n. — 14: type locality, stream SW of Vitina; 15: known distribution - holotype locality (white circle) and paratypes (black circle)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/278297/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

